<item>
            <title>[WFLY-878] Message-Driven Beans doesn&apos;t support DeliveryActive activation config property</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-878</link>
                <project id="12313721" key="WFLY">WildFly</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I get this warning on AS7.1.1 console, seems that ActivationConfigProperty DeliveryActive is not implemented by hornetq-ra, could we please have it as earlier JMS implementation of JMS had it &amp;amp; application that were using it will fail with AS7 now..?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;16:04:30,794 WARN  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;org.jboss.ejb3&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; (MSC service thread 1-16) JBAS014105: ActivationConfigProperty DeliveryActive will be ignored since it is not allowed by resource adapter: hornetq-ra&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks,&lt;br/&gt;
Prasad&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Windows 64 bit&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
